---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="py-16 px-6 border-t border-slate-800">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4">Responsible Use Statement</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
        I am committed to the ethical development of software. This includes prioritizing
        user data sovereignty, ensuring high accessibility standards, and a commitment to
        transparent, responsible technology use that augments human workflows without
        replacing human judgment.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center text-slate-500 text-sm">
      <p>&copy; {year} Luke Herrington. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
